projectGridLines.title: Project 1 Title: Data Science Intern
projectGridLines.description:
Project 1 Title: Data Science Intern


Description: Build Recommendation Systems

Skill sets: Python, Numpy, Pandas, Matplotlib

Traits expectation: Skilled in Data Science and Machine Learning techniques

Expected learning: The intern will learn about the application of Data Science in a SAAS

Specific courses required for project execution: Optimization, Non-Linear Optimization,

Mathematical Modelling, Game theory and its applications, Introduction to Mass

Communication.
